# Project KATANA

AI-assisted Japanese stock research and automated trading platform.

## Goal

Build a professional research platform for Japanese equities with:

- Data collection
- Backtesting
- Strategy optimization
- Paper trading
- Automated execution

Phase 1 focuses on research and backtesting before live trading.
